text: Rucentra grossepunctata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning and de Jong in 1941. It is known from Sumatra.BioLib.cz - Rucentra grossepunctata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Apomecynini Category:Beetles described in 1941
